GOAL build this modular so I can transform into my pubg voting map locations idea

* = implemented on both
& = implemented on pubg project only
/ = implemented on fcc project only


* authenticate with steam
/ allow authenticated user to access polls they created
* allow authenticated user to share with twitter via click and confirm
/ allow authenticated user to show all polls you created and their results on a single page as well as polls you've voted for and your vote
/ allow authenticated user to delete their polls
/ allow auth user to create poll with n number of items
/ non auth user can vote and see results IP LOCKED
/ auth user can vote and see results USERID LOCKED
/ auth users can add new options


